    public static enum ActionListenerI18n.I18nPalette
extends java.lang.Enum<ActionListenerI18n.I18nPalette>
    A palette for i18n. Use the lower-case constants for getting directly a BCP47 language tag.
    Author:
    Roland Bruggmann (brugr9@bfh.ch)
